1 0 0 1 50 786 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 772 Tm (This sets fully automatic backtest + paper logs without manual intervention.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 758 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 744 Tm (## Output files updated each run) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 730 Tm (- `data/live_ohlcv.csv`) Tj
