1 0 0 1 50 660 Tm (## Windows Task Scheduler) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 646 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 632 Tm (### 1\) Test manually once) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 618 Tm (```powershell) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 604 Tm (cd F:\\Trading) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 590 Tm (powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\\tools\\run_auto_backtest.ps1) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 576 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 562 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 548 Tm (### 2\) Register recurring task \(every 15 minutes\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 534 Tm (```powershell) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 520 Tm (cd F:\\Trading) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 506 Tm (powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\\deploy\\scheduler\\register_windows_task.ps1 -TaskName "IntratradeAutoBacktest" -Schedule MINUTE -Modifier 15 -StartTime "09:15") Tj
1 0 0 1 50 492 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 478 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 464 Tm (### 3\) Run on demand) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 450 Tm (```powershell) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 436 Tm (schtasks /Run /TN "IntratradeAutoBacktest") Tj
1 0 0 1 50 422 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 408 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 394 Tm (### 4\) Check status) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 380 Tm (```powershell) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 366 Tm (schtasks /Query /TN "IntratradeAutoBacktest" /V /FO LIST) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 352 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 338 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 324 Tm (### 5\) Delete task) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 310 Tm (```powershell) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 296 Tm (schtasks /Delete /TN "IntratradeAutoBacktest" /F) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 282 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 268 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 254 Tm (## Linux Cron \(if deployed on Linux\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 240 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 226 Tm (### 1\) Make runner executable) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 212 Tm (```bash) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 198 Tm (cd /opt/intratrade) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 184 Tm (chmod +x deploy/scheduler/run_auto_backtest.sh) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 170 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 156 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 142 Tm (### 2\) Add cron entry \(every 15 minutes\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 128 Tm (```bash) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 114 Tm (crontab -e) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 100 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 86 Tm (Add this line:) Tj
